How do you feel ?. I felt happy when i saw people receive the meal with a smile on there face. 
What did this experience teach you ?.
from this experience, i am thankful to my parent who have sacrifire themselve for me. I reliaze that i am more lucky than a lot of people out there. "Sharing is caring" 
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-35.2)</h3><p><div class="p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg border border-blue-100 flex items-center gap-4">
