(in the past).
(future). In the future, i want to go the moutains where is far away from city and help children in here. The children are often in poor condition lacking of fresh water, warm clothes, electricity, education and healthcare system.  (how ?). I think can bring some clothes for them, donate money to build the facilities, ... I hope that this can save more people in need. 
