I prefer small group. because we can spend more time with each others, have deep conversation, I can share my life, it is more private.</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-42.3)</h3><p><div class="p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg border border-blue-100 flex items-center gap-4">
