                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> How has socializing changed with phones? (cách mối quan hệ)
In the past, we used to meet face-to-face a lot. We spent a lot of time moving, money, effort for each other. This build deep connection between us.
Howerver, since the Internet, we use social media, chatting and online call instead. It is very convinient to connect. But this lacks of interaction (sự tương tác). 
+) trái đất phẳng (con người càng ngày cô đơn). 

